    "description": "The CFD model, calibrated against in-vitro bench measurements and validated per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements, reliably identifies the worst-case hemolysis operating condition among the five tested flow-speed combinations for the Class II CPB device.",
    "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-hemolysis-bench-2024",
